{"tid":11644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！屋企發現有木蝨","createTime":"2016-11-29T11:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T05:57:09.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"548d9ef25bffc66e3e857bf6b6fb4eefaaa00576","tid":11644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"求救 !<br />\n<br />\n9月中發現有野咬 我將所有床 床褥用蒸氣蒸同床上用品清洗 <br />\n<br />\n床板同床低所有野清潔哂 再噴木蝨水 <br />\n<br />\n兩晚後無再發現有野咬 呢兩日又黎過 但反轉哂都發現唔到有床蝨蹤影 <br />\n<br />\n吸埋床再清潔 真係咩都唔見 <br />\n<br />\n但半夜又有一隻活生生&amp;#21946;床上出現 究竟佢地匿&amp;#21946;邊?"},{"pid":"5cdfd1fad15479f801a6c7f10dae57c6518ea50c","tid":11644,"uid":16842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"床，枕頭，衣物，木製既家私"},{"pid":"bfc29c89f371c161d853f22f5a86dd2169a1e89f","tid":11644,"uid":31699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"相同情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係噴哂藥焗完落完DEBUG粉然後過幾日又有床蝨吸血<br />\n<br />\n巴打屋企係咪木地板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632a4d692e471bf9fa93ae29041c933850711237","tid":11644,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:22:06.000Z","msg":"搬得"},{"pid":"1baded421c20910833f918cef96f61aa66434b74","tid":11644,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"搵野炸下間房"},{"pid":"cf3f51dc0dd2669167e980d4f5389675917c40a3","tid":11644,"uid":16842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"我炸過3次都仲有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要打孖黎炸"},{"pid":"14380056c3139f9ce6f39d1bb49b02e76403ed3e","tid":11644,"uid":22122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"巴打住屋村定私樓？早幾年我條屋村木蝨成災，果時唔知發生咩事，淨係成日夜晚有野咬，當發現係木蝨時屋企已經有幾百隻。去個d環保鋪買d藥沖水成屋噴，幾乎掉哂屋企d傢俬，洗完d衫要放入膠袋以防班仆街lee係d衫度，搞左好耐情況先好轉。<br />\n但係都唔可以根治，間中都仲有出沒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c814c5cb2ec9a6f902158c90d742d9364e63d27d","tid":11644,"uid":16842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"巴打，<a href=\"http://tw.ptt01.cc/post_8849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.ptt01.cc%2Fpost_8849&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=3da622f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tw.ptt01.cc/post_8849</a><br />\n可以參考下"},{"pid":"f9ecf7a2ec111f4488a1b0cda703fe77d29b5546","tid":11644,"uid":18685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"認真， 搵滅蟲公司啦， 幾千蚊駛左佢， 如果唔係你所有木傢俬掉得"},{"pid":"6d8d71d806d14cafa818fab737a10eaf2b3c5293","tid":11644,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"搵專家搞啦"},{"pid":"b7a44eaf494aeffc3cd00f007efa038ebbbee245","tid":11644,"uid":6283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"完 換屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04e4f23f1708f7b95c7d8bfddbe5b324509e7e9","tid":11644,"uid":33383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:45:19.000Z","msg":"用藥對臭蟲無乜用 藥力堅既你住係果度你都死啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千零兩千蚊自己買部streamer 蒸均曬所有傢俬床褥枕頭就得<br />\n你搵滅蟲公司收你幾千蚊上門一次好多都只會咁做"},{"pid":"e97bf46b0181f626ef8c303dffa76cab1ca04b29","tid":11644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:25:53.000Z","msg":"琴晚噴完白僵菌睇下情況再算"},{"pid":"619198a95cc13f833bd64e2ba88fe18ad43eccf1","tid":11644,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"噴咗白僵菌後的確唔見木蝨出黎吸血"},{"pid":"9bef38171c1aa94ff2425b1f8b7ef2936b367f41","tid":11644,"uid":10505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"低價轉讓DE粉，無敵仕，白僵菌同kacher 蒸汽機"},{"pid":